headline: Hologic's Breast Health Unit Stays In Focus in 2026: What Lies Ahead?
summary: HOLX's Breast Health unit is back in focus as a proposed Blackstone-TPG deal adds a $76 cash offer and CVR to 2026-27 revenue goals.
